---
// Nuestra Filosofia Section
---

<section id="filosofia" class="py-24 bg-brand-bg relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-square md:aspect-[4/3] rounded-sm overflow-hidden grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 relative z-10 border border-white/5">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" 
            alt="El equipo trabajando" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Decorative bg -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-green/20 blur-3xl rounded-full z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Side -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white tracking-tight">Nuestra Filosofía</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          En GLE Marketing no somos agencias convencionales, somos socios estratégicos de tu negocio. Creemos en una visión a largo plazo donde combinamos el análisis, el diseño y la tecnología para generar resultados reales.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
          <div class="p-2">
            <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-brand-green mb-3 drop-shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)] leading-tight">94%</p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-wider">RETENCIÓN TOTAL</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-2">
            <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-brand-green mb-3 drop-shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(34,197,94,0.4)] leading-tight">10X</p>
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-wider">RETORNO ESTIMADO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
